00:45:30.088 --> 00:45:32.320
There are a lot of sort of
small pockets of things.

00:45:32.320 --> 00:45:35.900
I mean, there are several sort
of-- what do you call them?

00:45:35.900 --> 00:45:37.870
Non-profit institutions
that are sort of

00:45:37.870 --> 00:45:39.840
dedicated to addressing
some of these problems.

00:45:39.840 --> 00:45:43.710
There's like the Kaiser Family
Foundation, Robert Wood Johnson

00:45:43.710 --> 00:45:44.290
Foundation.

00:45:44.290 --> 00:45:46.260
A lot of times they
will give grants

00:45:46.260 --> 00:45:50.200
to various community level
programs, which are helpful.

00:45:50.200 --> 00:45:52.810
But again, we're
talking about limited--

00:45:52.810 --> 00:45:54.850
it's sort of like a small
piece of the puzzle.

00:45:54.850 --> 00:45:56.540
And so the issue is,
can we replicate these?

00:45:56.540 --> 00:45:58.540
Can we get the support we
