00:46:03.206 --> 00:46:04.960
But it's just like,
how do we sustain it?

00:46:04.960 --> 00:46:07.945
And how do we just-- once the
program's over, if you leave,

00:46:07.945 --> 00:46:09.570
then you're kind of
back where you are.

00:46:09.570 --> 00:46:13.150
How do we sustain
these initiatives?

00:46:13.150 --> 00:46:15.490
So I think there are a
lot of examples, actually.

00:46:15.490 --> 00:46:17.531
I didn't give you any one
specific one, but there

00:46:17.531 --> 00:46:18.448
